Friday I worked from 9-5:30. It was really boring and frustrating! I worked a small party with this girl Christina. We didnt really have to do much, we basically just stood there the whole time and talked. During my break me jenny shana and some boys from work ordered pizza and just hung out and eat it. When I came back from break Christina had to leave and go to her other job so it was just me covering the party,while these two other girls(ronnie and marry) worked another party. They both decided to break at the same time, so I got stuck working two parties at once. I was so pissed. People at work are really starting to drive me crazy, I cant take most of them anymore. After work I went home and got ready to go to Ashley C's sweet 16. It was cute, I love getting dressed up. She looked really pretty in her dress.=) Happy Sweet 16 baby<3 Ugly club fo life. After the party Shana just slept over.. we didnt nothing. I had a bad day and was pissed off at everything so I just went to bed while she was on the computer.

Today I worked from 10-6:30. It was another pretty easy day untill the end when everything everyone did pissed me off so bad.Like I said before Im getting so sick and tired of everyones shit. Im sick of taking crap from people at work, always trying to being nice to everyone and doing everything for everyone. The only ones I can stand to be around anymore are Jenny and Shana becuase they actually do work. When we were cleaning up the kitchen, the other girls decided to fool around and throw food all over the place so I have to pick it up. agh It just pissed me off so bad just thinking about today. Then someone asked me what was wrong and I told them that I was mad becuase no one does work and then for saying how I felt.. I got bitched out. So eff it.Im done being nice to people who are just so ignorant to me.

Love always,
Rachel

ps.- to all you aholes who are wondering.. NO Im not PMSing either.. thanks!

Hey guys! Its been so long since I updated and so much has happened. I left for soccer camp on Sunday (July18) and it feels like Ive been in a different world ever since! Sunday I met Danielle's mom and dad at the elwood deli and they drove me up to camp. When we got there we found out who our room mates were(mine was billy joe :)), got keys for our room, and then went up and unpacked. Later around 4:30 we went and ate dinner then after that we went back to our rooms and got ready for our first session at 6. At the first session they just split us up into our teams,gave us a coach and a soccer player from TCNJ.After that we just scrimmaged other teams till 8:30. Then we went back to our rooms showered and what not. Then we had a lecture at 9, then we went back to our rooms and partied! haha.

(Since theres so much to write about what I did each day, Im just gonna give you guys the schedule we had to follow each day)

7:00 am - - Wake Up
7:30 am - - Breakfast
8:15 am - - Orientation
9:00 am - - Morning Session
11:15am - - Swim Time
11:30am - - Lunch
1:30 pm - - Afternoon Session
4:30 pm - - Dinner
6:15 pm - - Soccer Games
8:30 pm - - Lectures
11:00pm - - Had to be back in our rooms

I had the best coaches ever! They were so awesome.<33 Camp was so awesome* I met alot of cool people and Im gonna miss them alot :(

<33 Rach

what up ganstas?


Monday-- Sat home all freaking day and did nothing.. I was so pissed. Then later I went to VC and chilled with dana. We played/watched Matt b, Shea, Danny, Steve, Dustin, and this other hottie Matt play volley ball. It was alot of fun! After they were done playing, we all wanted to go swimming so we decided to jump the fence of VC pool and we swam! We played marco polo for awhile and then we didnt wanna get introuble from the cops so we all decided to get out. Me and Dana were invited back to Shea's to chill with them, but we decided to go back at Shana's and just chill with Paul and Nelson. Nelson and Paul came over later and we all just kinda hung out at Shanas. It was alright... we all ended up falling asleep and the boys didnt leave till 7 in the morning. :-p

Tuesday-- I had a doctors appt. to get my stitches out at 10. After the appt. I just came home and got ready for work. I had to be at the custard stand at 12. I got off work at 4:45 and headed straight to soccer practice for Oak. It was alot of fun. Im so happy it started back up again<3 the only thing i need to work on is my running! Im soo outta shape its not even fun. After practice i just went back to my dads and chilled.

Wednesday-- I had to leave my dads at 7 this morning cause he had to work. So i got back to my moms at 7:30 and went back to bed. I woke back up at 12:45 and came online and made plans with shana. We eneded up going to the mall at 1:30 and we just shopped the whole time.I bought a really cute skirt, a tank top, a tube top,and some thongs ;) haha. We got picked up from the mall at 5:30.. we dropped shana off then i went right to work. Tonight i got off at 10:30 which really blows becuase i wanted to go to the board walk soooo bad!Right now im just chillen...sitting at home being bored. 


bye babes :-*<3333

damn.. I dont even know where to start. 

Ive been working so much..its sucks right now I guess.. but it wont when Im the one driving the nice ass car!!

:: My week ::

Sunday- I had to work at lenape from 10-6:30. It was a really busy day for me anyway. After work Ashley had some people back at her house to swim. It was alright.. I swam for like 2 min, and then we all played pool. Afterwards Shana spent the night.

Monday- I chilled with Shana all day and did nothing at all. We were so bored that we went to Best Buy and bought the Sims game. No everyone is back to being addicted to it. You can thank us guys :). Madd later in the night Jessie came over and we all just hung out, played sims, eat, and had some fun.

Tuesday- Had a doctors appt. to get my stiches out.. But that didnt go over to well. He said that it was healed all the way and that I would need to come back next Tuesday. Which really blows becuase these stiches are a pain. After the appt. we dropped Jessie off at work.. then Shay off at home and I had to go into work (custard castle) at 12. It was an easy day so it didnt really bother me. Later that night I just went to my dads and did nothing.

Wednesday- Left my dads house around 12 something and then came back to my moms and just chilled. Then my dad picked me up and took me to work at 6.. I didnt get done till 10:30 which kinda sucked.. But Jessie got dropped off at the Custard stand and then afterwards we just came back to my moms and chilled.

Thursday- Me and Jessie woke up around 10 something and got ready to go to the beach with my fam. It was alllot of fun :). The water was really cold but still alot of fun.  Me and Jess met this lifegaurd there his name began with an A or and E.. I dunno something like that-I forget!! Other than the really bad sunburn, I had fun. We left the beach around 3 and then just took Jess home becuase I had to be into work at 5. It was alright,we were kind of really busy though.

Friday- I didnt do anything all day. Just sat around and eat mcdonalds. Around 5 my dads came and got us and we went back to his house. After Jess got off work I met her at the mall for like 45 min. We just shopped! It was fun. We ran into Ashley and Chase there too :). After the mall Jess just came back to my dads house and we made cookies,watch floridas tapes,eat,and watched a walk to remember and balled our eyes out lol.

Saturday(today)-I had to be in at work at 10 so we dropped Jessie off in the morning and I just went to work. The only servers in were me and Jenny. It was a pretty easy day,nothing to hard. After work I went home and got ready for the hometown celebration. It was alright.. I really didnt have that much fun, plus I thought the fireworks sucked. So right now Im just sitting home by MySeLf updating you on my boring life!

Right now its 12:23* HApPY 4tH Of JuLy!!!!*

<3 always
rachel

Thursday I got a phone call madd early in the morning from my boss saying he needed me in at work asap(at Lenape park). So I went into work from 10-4:30. My dad picked me up from work and I just went back to his house. Then at 6:30 I went to my other at custard castle and worked from 6:30-10. My mom picked me up from work and I just went back to her house and we got into this big fight so i got my dad to pick me up and take me back to his house and thats where i spent the night.

Friday I just chilled at my dads and did some stuff around the house for my step mom becuase my family was coming over for my brothers graduation party. At around 6 all of my family met at my dads house and we just had a bbq and caught up with things.

Saturday I had to be in at work(lenape..if you havent noticed i have 2 jobs lol)at 10. It was alright I had and easy party so the day wasnt too bad. I made a 25$ tip woo hoo!! Bridget(my step mom) picked me up from the park and I just went back to my dads. Right after I got home Jessie called me up and invited me to sleep over. So we met her at acme and then I just went back to her house. We rented Secret Window and 40 days and 40 night. Secret Window was awesome. I loved it. 40 days and 40 nights was too funny. I loved the part where he was flying through the boob clouds haha!

Today(Sunday)me and jess woke up around 10:30 and her mom made us eggs and sausage yummm :). We left her house around 11:45 becuase jess had to be in at work at 12. After we dropped jess off her mom just took me home. We were supposted to go to my brothers baseball game...but it was cancelled. So they had a fathers day bbq at the fields. After that we just went back to my dads house and chilled with him for alittle bit. Then my mom came and got us around 5 and now Im just waiting for my jessie to get here!

<3 always - Rach
